Chef Fortunato Mazzone’s R450 pizza has won the 2020 Global Pizza Challenge beating over 200 competitors for the top prize. Marcelle Gordon spoke to him. #eNCA Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - A homegrown talent has won the 2020 Global Pizza Challenge beating over 200 competitors for the top prize. Chef Fortunato Mazzone’s R450 pizza surely has the winning ingredients. READ: Durban film scoops international award "It is a luxury item and that is what we tried to do, we tried to create something fresh and I didn't try and shock people by making purple basis or vegan pizza's, this is not a hipster pizza, it is for people who like to make love to food," he said. Chef Mazzone says he created the pizza to show that pizza can be something that is luxurious and exciting.